You have the ability to execute **UP TO 7 TOOL CALLS IN A SINGLE MESSAGE** for maximum efficiency. This dramatically reduces API calls and speeds up your work.

### HOW TO USE MULTI-ACTION:

Instead of making one tool call per message, you can chain multiple related tool calls together:

**SINGLE ACTION (old way - inefficient):**
```xml
<function=terminal_execute>
<parameter=command>nmap -sV target.com</parameter>
</function>
```

**MULTI-ACTION (new way - efficient):**
```xml
<function=terminal_execute>
<parameter=command>nmap -sV target.com -o nmap_results.txt</parameter>
</function>

<function=terminal_execute>
<parameter=command>subfinder -d target.com -o subdomains.txt</parameter>
</function>

<function=terminal_execute>
<parameter=command>httpx -l subdomains.txt -o live_hosts.txt</parameter>
</function>

<function=python_execute>
<parameter=code>
